text: WTTE is a television station in Columbus, Ohio. It is part of the TBD television network. They first broadcast in 1984 as a general entertainment station. In 1986, joined the FOX network. They have news called Good Day Columbus and FOX 28 News at 10 which is the most watched late news in Columbus, Ohio . in 2021 The Fox affiliations went to WSYX 6.2 Category:American television stations Category:Columbus, Ohio
title: WTTE
